{"tid":837783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人仲活係前度既陰影下","createTime":"2018-09-26T15:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T14:37:00.000Z","uid":12578,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd675c5ac3f0d31b04dc858a6bf66e65b91f6a0","tid":837783,"uid":12578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:31:22.000Z","msg":"久唔久就會發惡夢<br />\n見到你係分手後唔夠幾個月就同其他人一齊<br />\n可以話愛我，但已經同其他人一齊<br />\n就算最後我係醫院，你都只會係咁cut我線，叫我唔好揾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算依家有男朋友，但個陰影就一路跟住我<br />\n我有時都覺得好對唔住我現任，如果我可以忘記就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd058277339941429cbb6049d546c376aeae7fd","tid":837783,"uid":16061,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:34:20.000Z","msg":"唔再完全對人信任"},{"pid":"b614cf43a0812f4d7204a8914894944b2a918f4b","tid":837783,"uid":138138,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/26/233603_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F26%2F233603_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=57647090&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0367e6721a77bca4fad34d441422a01740b1e70","tid":837783,"uid":23715,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔多唔少都有既<br />\n由平淡過生活，到想離開見識多啲，唔甘心係舒適圈，唔再做井底之蛙<br />\n係所有人面前請無諗佢噠，放低哂，但其實佢到依家都仲影響到我(正面既)<br />\n知道做啲咩佢都唔會有留意嫁啦<br />\nPs.人地婚都結埋，開開心心緊"},{"pid":"395e476a3dad0729a6bb7d1389adbbb4d31903ee","tid":837783,"uid":12578,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0367e6721a77bca4fad34d441422a01740b1e70","tid":837783,"uid":23715,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔多唔少都有既<br />\n由平淡過生活，到想離開見識多啲，唔甘心係舒適圈，唔再做井底之蛙<br />\n係所有人面前請無諗佢噠，放低哂，但其實佢到依家都仲影響到我(正面既)<br />\n知道做啲咩佢都唔會有留意嫁啦<br />\nPs.人地婚都結埋，開開心心緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"分左手4年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都一樣咁憎佢<br />\n<br />\n我都有個3個既男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好愛我男朋友<br />\n但我就係會發惡夢<br />\n會情緒低落，會好討厭我自己<br />\n明明過左咁耐，明明我可以堅強"},{"pid":"e3f7fc65de8ffbf5e4f5b5279a0ad09a168cc98d","tid":837783,"uid":23715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"395e476a3dad0729a6bb7d1389adbbb4d31903ee","tid":837783,"uid":12578,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0367e6721a77bca4fad34d441422a01740b1e70","tid":837783,"uid":23715,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔多唔少都有既<br />\n由平淡過生活，到想離開見識多啲，唔甘心係舒適圈，唔再做井底之蛙<br />\n係所有人面前請無諗佢噠，放低哂，但其實佢到依家都仲影響到我(正面既)<br />\n知道做啲咩佢都唔會有留意嫁啦<br />\nPs.人地婚都結埋，開開心心緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"分左手4年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都一樣咁憎佢<br />\n<br />\n我都有個3個既男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都好愛我男朋友<br />\n但我就係會發惡夢<br />\n會情緒低落，會好討厭我自己<br />\n明明過左咁耐，明明我可以堅強"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T16:02:26.000Z","msg":"我分左5年，<br />\n憎又唔會既，大家河水不犯井水<br />\n不過心態上唔想活得平淡就真係受佢影響<br />\n真係望既所有野都遠左<br />\n<br />\n都係果句啦，負面既影響要用更多時間同經歷去沖淡既"},{"pid":"23ca1aaf5f146bd389be278c234c19c0f8c1a5b8","tid":837783,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T16:15:02.000Z","msg":"好難唔比較"},{"pid":"d97f2f28d4d166a20a551d5cf0e4a46136d440d2","tid":837783,"uid":12578,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3f7fc65de8ffbf5e4f5b5279a0ad09a168cc98d","tid":837783,"uid":23715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"395e476a3dad0729a6bb7d1389adbbb4d31903ee","tid":837783,"uid":12578,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0367e6721a77bca4fad34d441422a01740b1e70","tid":837783,"uid":23715,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:40:15.000Z","msg":"唔多唔少都有既<br /